
Ranger Help for: camp
=====================

SYNTAX:      camp
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   1
BASE SP:     1/4 max sp
SKILL TYPE:  aid 

SUMMARY:    
Rangers do not have a guild hall. All of the wilderness is their guild hall.
As a result, Rangers do not have a place that they can take their stuff and
store while they are away. But being the masters of the wild that they are,
Rangers have learned how to rough it in the outdoors. When a Ranger 'camps',
they create a small campsite and makeshift tent. In it they store their
stuff so when they come back, its all redy for them to explore. Camping
also saves a Rangers position. Campsites won't last over reboots.

